Package: lightum
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, dbus, upower, systemd-services, xbacklight
Description: MacBook automatic light sensor daemon
 This program adjusts the keyboard brightness and screen
 backlight on MacBook laptops, it does it by reading the
 light sensor value reported by the front camera (iSight).
